title: Mamma White's Pancake Parlour
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers vegan pancakes with lots of fresh fruit toppings, maple syrup and some veggie toppings. Small family friendly cafe with activities provided for children. Online menu doesn't list vegan choices although there are some besides pancakes.
